===Etymology===
From the {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|cenyth}}, from the {{etyl|ML.|en}} {{term|cenit|lang=la}}, a transliteration of the {{etyl|ar|en}} {{m|ar|سَمْت||direction, path}} which is in itself a weak abbreviation of {{m|ar|سَمْت الرَأْس||direction of the head}}.

